{"tid":1967152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳答問題可獲500元現金券　百佳澄清並無此事","createTime":"2020-04-10T16:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T16:50:36.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"45d4f2b7d67b9ccff1fc112fbd1bb8e5292549d2","tid":1967152,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmFzGc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmFzGc0.jpg&h=86ed7dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新冠肺炎疫情假消息滿天飛，有市民曾因斷貨消息而到超級市場搶購日用品。而近日再有消息廣泛流傳，稱市民只需登入特定網站答問題，則可免費獲得百佳超級市場的500元現金券。百佳今日(10日)晚上在社交網站上發文澄清，並無相關推廣活動。<br />\n<br />\n近日WhatsApp廣傳一則優惠推廣信息，並聲稱市民只需登入相關訊息中附上的一個網站連結，回答簡單問題後，再將訊息轉發予20個朋友或5個群組，則可獲得500元的百佳現金券。<br />\n<br />\n百佳今晚在社交媒體上發文，特此聲明並沒有此推廣活動，並呼籲顧客提高警覺。又稱如有疑問可致電客戶服務熱線26068658或私信他們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTSFBMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTSFBMq.jpg&h=1bf6db31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200410/mobile/bkn-20200410200502250-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200410200502250-0410_00822_001.html&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479Vf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=68340639\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200410/mobile/bkn-20200410200502250-0410_00822_001.html</a>"}]}